u(z)=0}
u(z)\{\kappa_a(v\mid z)-\widetilde\kappa_a(v\mid z)\}=0.\] For a library kernel, nonnegativity on supported assignments implies \(q^{\mathrm{obs}}_{h,a}(v,a)\ge0\), and normalization gives \[\sum_{v\in\mathcal V}q^{\mathrm{obs}}_{h,a}(v,a)=\sum_{z:
u(z)>0}
u(z)\sum_v\kappa_{h,a}(v\mid z)=\sum_{z:
u(z)>0}
